{"tid":584502,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩辦法可以早啲陽痿","createTime":"2018-03-08T00:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T06:25:12.000Z","uid":90457,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"60d89f94796c7d9f05c6e87f7aaa86a453800c55","tid":584502,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"條朘真係好唔聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知咩情況，有時喺冇諗鹹濕嘢嘅情況吓自己豎起，尤其喺車裡面訓醒後，落車驚覺條毛攝喺包皮同龜頭之間，扯起上嚟每行一步就好似俾嘢劏一刀嘅感覺，真係好痛，但我冇理由當眾伸手入條褲裡面搞掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早排表妹同佢屋企人嚟拜年，我明明冇對佢想入非非，我發誓。。。但我條朘又搞搞陣，我呀媽叫我行出去幫我細佬裝飯（佢08出世年未夠高裝到飯）我都唔敢起身驚俾我表妹見到，我遲遲唔肯起身點知我細佬當住咁多人面前展露奸邪笑容同我講<br />\n「大概只有男仔先會明你發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n反正我都冇扑嘢嘅福氣，扯旗除咗令我有能力打飛機傷身之外仲帶嚟好多生活上嘅不便，咁我仲扯嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e172f2f108ba7592db2d7e012547864ef233e23","tid":584502,"uid":138197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"切左佢"},{"pid":"a2c5b3494be013cb9f8ae6078103fdb94b678d6d","tid":584502,"uid":138197,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1e172f2f108ba7592db2d7e012547864ef233e23","tid":584502,"uid":138197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"切左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"切埋右 thanks 肥婆咪入黎"},{"pid":"5b0562ff888acd08c89bb13c1129a5a265fb7ff5","tid":584502,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:41:42.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"8c11196d7e087c398949895d352b74b6cacf1a7f","tid":584502,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1e172f2f108ba7592db2d7e012547864ef233e23","tid":584502,"uid":138197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"切左佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:42:00.000Z","msg":"認真